    under the table..\r\n\r\nCrystalpher: (Can\u2019t speak. I lost my ability to
    speak.)\r\n\r\nCrystalpher: (And even if I could I do not have the anatomy to
    speak.)\r\n\r\nCrystalpher: (I would like to have something simple that could
    speed me up.)\n\nCrystalpher: (This old soul has a hard time moving around quickly...)\r\n"
